item.title: Dutch Nao Team
item.description: I am part of the Dutch Nao Team, participating in the RoboCup Standard Platform League. I’ve been on multiple trips with my team, which has gotten me in quite a lot of different places: Techfest IIT, Mumbai, India (2015-2016) RoboCup European Open, Eindhoven, Netherlands (2016) RoboCup Leipzig, Germany (2016) RoHOW, Hamburg, Germany (2016) RoboCup Iran Open, Teheran, Iran (2017) RoboCup Nagoya, Japan (2017) RoHOW, Hamburg, Germany (2017) [TBD] RoboCup Montreal, Canada (2018)
